          "body": {
            "text": "The crag is on the left-hand side of road 225 when driving towards Fituna, just before the turning for Grödinge kyrka and Skanssundet. The wall rises behind the trees on the far side of a potato field.\n\nOld coordinates: 10 I SV 615150",
